quote&gt;\r\n&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;strong&gt;d.&lt;/strong&gt; ANY IMPLIED WARRANTY ARISING FROM\r\nCOURSE OF DEALING OR USAGE OF TRADE; AND \r\n&lt;/blockquote&gt;\r\n&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;strong&gt;e.&lt;/strong&gt; ANY OBLIGATION, LIABILITY, RIGHT,\r\nCLAIM, OR REMEDY IN TORT, WHETHER OR NOT ARISING FROM THE NEGLIGENCE\r\nOF Oliotr OR Oliotr PAYMENTS. &lt;br&gt;\r\nTO THE FULL EXTENT PERMISSIBLE\r\nUNDER APPLICABLE LAW, Oliotr AND Oliotr PAYMENTS DISCLAIM ANY AND ALL\r\nSUCH WARRANTIES.&lt;/blockquote&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;GeneralRelease&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;16. General Release.&lt;/strong&gt;\r\nBECAUSE Oliotr AND Oliotr PAYMENTS ARE NOT INVOLVED IN TRANSACTIONS\r\nBETWEEN BUYERS AND SELLERS OR OTHER PARTICIPANT DEALINGS, IF A\r\nDISPUTE ARISES BETWEEN ONE OR MORE PARTICIPANTS, EACH OF YOU RELEASE\r\nOliotr AND Oliotr PAYMENTS (AND THEIR RESPECTIVE AGENTS AND\r\nEMPLOYEES) FROM CLAIMS, DEMANDS, AND DAMAGES (ACTUAL AND\r\nCONSEQUENTIAL) OF EVERY KIND AND NATURE, KNOWN AND UNKNOWN, SUSPECTED\r\nAND UNSUSPECTED, DISCLOSED AND UNDISCLOSED, ARISING OUT OF OR IN ANY\r\nWAY CONNECTED WITH SUCH DISPUTES.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;IndemnityLimitationofLiability&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;17.\r\nIndemnity/Limitation of Liability.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;strong&gt;a. Indemnity and Defense.&lt;/strong&gt; You will\r\ndefend, indemnify and hold harmless Oliotr, Oliotr Payments, and each\r\nof their affiliates (and their respective employees, directors,\r\nagents and representatives) from and against any and all claims,\r\ncosts, losses, damages, judgments, penalties, interest and expenses\r\n(including reasonable attorneys\' fees) arising out of any Claim that\r\narises out of or relates to: (i) any actual or alleged breach of your\r\nrepresentations, warranties, or obligations set forth in this\r\nParticipation Agreement; or (ii) your own website or other sales\r\nchannels, the products you sell, any conten