lying Buyers or Sellers. \r\n&lt;/blockquote&gt;\r\n&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;strong&gt;c. Severability.&lt;/strong&gt; If any provision of\r\nthis Participation Agreement shall be deemed unlawful, void, or for\r\nany reason unenforceable, then that provision shall be deemed\r\nseverable from these terms and conditions and shall not affect the\r\nvalidity and enforceability of any remaining provisions. \r\n&lt;/blockquote&gt;\r\n&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;strong&gt;d. No Waiver.&lt;/strong&gt; Neither Oliotr nor Oliotr\r\nPayments will be considered to have waived any of its rights or\r\nremedies described in this Participation Agreement unless the waiver\r\nis in writing and signed by the relevant party. No delay or omission\r\nby Oliotr or Oliotr Payments in exercising its rights or remedies\r\nwill impair or be construed as a waiver. Any single or partial\r\nexercise of a right or remedy will not preclude further exercise of\r\nany other right or remedy. Oliotr\'s or Oliotr Payments\' failure to\r\nenforce the strict performance of any provision of this Participation\r\nAgreement will not constitute a waiver of either party\'s right to\r\nsubsequently enforce such provision or any other provisions of this\r\nParticipation Agreement.&lt;/blockquote&gt;\r\n\r\n',	'Participation Agreement',	'',	'');
