(62,	1,	' CONCENTRATED DETERGENT POWDER ',	'&lt;p&gt;Premium detergent powder with multiple enzyme system to remove the most \r\nstubborn stains and dirt deposits effortlessly, maintaining the colour \r\nand texture of the fabric.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;accordion-section&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;accordion-section-title active&quot; href=&quot;https://www.modicare.com/ProductLanding.aspx?p=GwtPcYkOGcM=&amp;amp;grp=Iey5Mcr6SMI=&amp;amp;pattern=Iey5Mcr6SMI=#accordion1&quot;&gt; features &amp;amp; benefits&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;accordion1&quot; class=&quot;accordion-section-content open&quot; style=&quot;display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Powerzymes:&amp;nbsp; &lt;/strong&gt;Greater stain busting power. Cuts through the toughest of stains with ease.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Powerful Active Oxygen: &lt;/strong&gt;Quickly &amp;amp; deeply penetrate the layers of fabric and directly attack the stains to break them down.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fabric Bleaching Activators: &lt;/strong&gt;Activate bleaching action even at low temperature without affecting the colour &amp;amp; texture of the fabric.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Softening Agent: &lt;/strong&gt;Reduce water hardness &amp;amp; enhance washing.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optical Brighteners: &lt;/strong&gt;Provide super brightness to the clothes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Anti re-deposition agents:&lt;/strong&gt; Prevent re-deposition of dirt on clothes during wash.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Anti corrosive agents: &lt;/strong&gt;Protect rusting of metallic parts of washing machine &amp;amp; clothes like zip, metallic buttons, etc.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Require less water to rinse. Saves water, time and energy.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;accordion-section-title active&quot; href=&quot;https://www.modicare.com/ProductLanding.aspx?p=GwtPcYkOGcM=&amp;amp;grp=Iey5Mcr6SMI=&amp;amp;pattern=Iey5Mcr6SMI=#accordion2&quot;&gt;usage directions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;accordion2&quot; class=&quot;accordion-section-content open&quot; style=&quot;display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bucket Wash:&lt;/strong&gt; 1 Scoop &lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Machine Wash (Top &amp;amp;&amp;nbsp;Front Loading): &lt;/strong&gt;2 Scoops&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;br&gt;\r\nFor better quality of wash, soak clothes for at least 30 minutes in detergent solution and wash as usual&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;accordion-section&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;accordion-section-title active&quot; href=&quot;https://www.modicare.com/ProductLanding.aspx?p=GwtPcYkOGcM=&amp;amp;grp=Iey5Mcr6SMI=&amp;amp;pattern=Iey5Mcr6SMI=#accordion3&quot;&gt; caution&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;accordion3&quot; class=&quot;accordion-section-content open&quot; style=&quot;display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Not recommended for Silk &amp;amp; Woolens clothes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;For new clothes do a patch test for colour running with small amount of detergent solution before washing&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;accordion4&quot; class=&quot;accordion-section-content open&quot; style=&quot;display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Objective: &lt;/strong&gt;To show the oil removing ability of Washmate Concentrated Detergent Powder (Original Formula).&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Materials Required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Washmate Concentrated Detergent Powder (Original Formula)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2 glass tumblers with water&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Teaspoon&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Baby talcum powder&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Materials Required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Washmate Concentrated Detergent Powder (Original Formula)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fill two glass tumblers with water. Add approx. ¼ teaspoon of \r\nWashmate Concentrated Detergent Powder (Original Formula) to the first \r\ntumbler.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Stir well to dissolve detergent.Skim off any excess foam so that the surface of the liquid in both the tumblers is clear.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sprinkle an equal amount of talcum powder on the surface of the liquid in both the tumblers.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Result&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;The talcum powder sprinkled on the surface of the second tumbler\r\n continues to float on the surface. The talcum powder sprinkled on the \r\nWashmate detergent solution quickly becomes wet and sinks to the bottom \r\nof the tumbler.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;(Scented talcum powder is a mixture of oily fragrance and white \r\nclay. This represents the soil, dirt and grime on the used clothing. The\r\n oil fragrance mixture uniformly coats each particle of the clay and \r\nprevents plain water from penetrating and wetting it and the talcum \r\ncontinues to float on the surface of water. But the powerful surfactant \r\nin Washmate Concentrated Detergent Powder (Original Formula) penetrates \r\nand removes the oil in the talcum).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;',	' CONCENTRATED DETERGENT POWDER ',	' CONCENTRATED DETERGENT POWDER ',	' CONCENTRATED DETERGENT POWDER ',	' CONCENTRATED DETERGENT POWDER '),
