ks, bed frames, door knobs, telephone instruments, bathrooms, \r\nlavatories, shower cubicles, nappy buckets, garbage bins, etc.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Can be used even for sanitising food contact surfaces&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Good for use in hospitals, clinics, restaurants, meat / chicken / fish processing units, dairy / poultry farms&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;',	'CLEANER',	'STERICLEAN - DISINFECTANT CLEANER',	'STERICLEAN - DISINFECTANT CLEANER',	'STERICLEAN - DISINFECTANT CLEANER'),
