(64,	1,	' DELICATE LIQUID DETERGENT ',	'&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Liquid Detergent for Woolen &amp;amp; Delicate Fabrics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;\r\nUnique international formula for gentle and effective washing of \r\nwashable silks, chiffons, sweaters, baby clothes, lingerie etc. at home.\r\n It maintains the colour and texture of the fabrics while removing dirt \r\nand stains from clothes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;accordion-section&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;accordion-section-title active&quot; href=&quot;https://www.modicare.com/ProductLanding.aspx?p=iXj4e3Q9m8k=&amp;amp;grp=Iey5Mcr6SMI=&amp;amp;pattern=Iey5Mcr6SMI=#accordion1&quot;&gt; features &amp;amp; benefits&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;accordion1&quot; class=&quot;accordion-section-content open&quot; style=&quot;display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gentle on woolen and delicate clothes:&lt;/strong&gt; Very effective on washable silks, chiffons, rayon, lingerie, woolens, hosiery items, baby clothes, etc.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Powerful performance:&lt;/strong&gt; Gently and effortlessly lifts off dirt deposits maintaining colour and texture of the fabric.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Highly concentrated:&lt;/strong&gt; Very less quantity required per use&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pleasant fragrance:&lt;/strong&gt; Leaves clothes mildly fragrant&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;accordion-section-title active&quot; href=&quot;https://www.modicare.com/ProductLanding.aspx?p=iXj4e3Q9m8k=&amp;amp;grp=Iey5Mcr6SMI=&amp;amp;pattern=Iey5Mcr6SMI=#accordion2&quot;&gt;usage directions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;accordion2&quot; class=&quot;accordion-section-content open&quot; style=&quot;display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bucket Wash:&lt;/strong&gt;10ml&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;br&gt;\r\nDissolve required quantity (10ml) of liquid detergent in water.  Soak \r\nclothes for 5 to 10 minutes. Gently squeeze out foam. Rinse in  plain \r\nwater.&amp;nbsp; Do not wring. Dry flat&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Machine Wash (Top loading):&lt;/strong&gt; 20ml&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;br&gt;\r\nAdd required quantity (20ml) of liquid detergent to the washing machine.\r\n Wash garments in gentle mode. Rinse in plain water.&amp;nbsp; Do not spin. Dry \r\nflat&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;For better wash, soak clothes for 5 to 10 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;accordion-section-title active&quot; href=&quot;https://www.modicare.com/ProductLanding.aspx?p=iXj4e3Q9m8k=&amp;amp;grp=Iey5Mcr6SMI=&amp;amp;pattern=Iey5Mcr6SMI=#accordion3&quot;&gt;caution&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;accordion3&quot; class=&quot;accordion-section-content open&quot; style=&quot;display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Make sure the fabric is colourfast and washable.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Follow garment manufacturers label instructions.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;',	' DELICATE LIQUID DETERGENT ',	' DELICATE LIQUID DETERGENT ',	' DELICATE LIQUID DETERGENT ',	' DELICATE LIQUID DETERGENT '),
(65,	1,	' WASHMATE PRE-WASH DIRT AND STAIN REMOVER ',	'&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Give your clothes the new pre-treatment for effective washing. Unique \r\nstain busting formula with enzymes removes tough stains like oil, \r\ngrease, motor oil, blood, grass, tea, coffee, etc. Contain five stain \r\nremoving agents for effective cleaning. Gently loosens soil and dirt \r\nfrom cuffs, collars and saree falls. Scrub free formula reduces wear and\r\n tear of clothes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;accordion-section&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;accordion-section-title active&quot; href=&quot;https://www.modicare.com/ProductLanding.aspx?p=POzRhBaXmwM=&amp;amp;grp=Iey5Mcr6SMI=&amp;amp;pattern=Iey5Mcr6SMI=#accordion1&quot;&gt; features &amp;amp; benefits&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;accordion1&quot; class=&quot;accordion-section-content open&quot; style=&quot;display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scrub free formula: &lt;/strong&gt;Works quickly to loosen tough stains, cuff and collar soil, dirt, grime etc.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Five different stain removing agents including enzymes:&lt;/strong&gt;Helps\r\n remove tough stains (like oil, grease, motor oil, blood, grass, \r\nproteins, tea, coffee, ketch-up, curry, ink,&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; lipstick, make-up etc.)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Convenient spill-proof pack with nozzle plug:&lt;/strong&gt; Easy to use. No leakage, no wastage. Reaches target area with ease. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;accordion-section-title active&quot; href=&quot;https://www.modicare.com/ProductLanding.aspx?p=POzRhBaXmwM=&amp;amp;grp=Iey5Mcr6SMI=&amp;amp;pattern=Iey5Mcr6SMI=#accordion2&quot;&gt;usage directions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;accordion2&quot; class=&quot;accordion-section-content open&quot; style=&quot;display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Apply\r\n on dry dirty or stained area before wetting clothes, wait for 5 to 10 \r\nminutes and wash as usual with detergent powder (preferably with \r\nWashmate detergent powders)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Use on dry stains.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tough &amp;amp; old stains may require more than one application.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;accordion-section-title active&quot; href=&quot;https://www.modicare.com/ProductLanding.aspx?p=POzRhBaXmwM=&amp;amp;grp=Iey5Mcr6SMI=&amp;amp;pattern=Iey5Mcr6SMI=#accordion3&quot;&gt;caution&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;accordion3&quot; class=&quot;accordion-section-content open&quot; style=&quot;display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Make sure the fabric is colourfast and washable.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Not to be used on silks and woolens.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;accordion-section&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;accordion-section-title active&quot; href=&quot;https://www.modicare.com/ProductLanding.aspx?p=POzRhBaXmwM=&amp;amp;grp=Iey5Mcr6SMI=&amp;amp;pattern=Iey5Mcr6SMI=#accordion4&quot;&gt; demonstration&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;accordion4&quot; class=&quot;accordion-section-content open&quot; style=&quot;display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Objective: To show the superior dirt and stain removing power of Washmate Pre-Wash&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Material Required&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fabric swatches&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dirty motor oil / soya sauce&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dropper&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Glass tumbler&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Washmate Pre-Wash Dirt and Stain Remover&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Water&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Method&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Stain the centre of the swatch with 2 - 3 drops of dirty motor \r\noil / soya sauce.Allow 15 minutes for it to thoroughly penetrate the \r\nfabric.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Apply Washmate Pre-Wash on the stain.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;After 5 minutes immerse the treated swatch in the tumbler containing water. Secure the cap / lid.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Shake the tumbler for 2 to 3 minutes to simulate machine washing action.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Note that the stain treated with Washmate Pre-Wash has been substantially removed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Remove the swatch.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;',	' WASHMATE PRE-WASH DIRT AND STAIN REMOVER ',	' WASHMATE PRE-WASH DIRT AND STAIN REMOVER ',	' WASHMATE PRE-WASH DIRT AND STAIN REMOVER ',	' WASHMATE PRE-WASH DIRT AND STAIN REMOVER '),
