(68,	1,	' WELL MULTIVITAMIN MULTIMINERAL ',	'&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot; style=&quot;text-align:left;&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Features &amp;amp; Benefits&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;•&amp;nbsp;Provides the necessary nutrients that helps in bridging the nutritional gap&lt;br&gt;•&amp;nbsp;Provides 12 essential vitamins &amp;amp; 11 important minerals&lt;br&gt;•&amp;nbsp;Provides 6 important phytonutrients &amp;amp; 2 amino acids&lt;br&gt;•&amp;nbsp;Contains “Piperine” that helps increase bioavailability of nutrients&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Potential Users&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;People who&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Do not eat fresh fruits, vegetables, whole grains every day.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Smoke,\r\n chew tobacco, drink alcohol or are subject to physiological stress and \r\npollution, these can deplete the body of essential nutrients.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Often skip meals or compromise on eating highly processed food.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Are on dieting.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Are not aware of the nutrition they get from the food they eat and want toget essential nutrients daily.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;General Information&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Unhealthy\r\n eating habits effects are manifold. They can lead to a whole mess of \r\ndisorders and health problems.The modern and hectic life style often \r\nleads to unhealthy eating habits that deny our body proper nutrition. \r\nThis could be in the form of skipped meals, crash diets or eating highly\r\n processed foods that may be low on nutrition.Our regular diets may also\r\n lack in proper nutrition and can come under scanner due to food being \r\nhighly cooked or fried that destroys the nutritional value of food. \r\nMoreover the absence of variety of fruits, vegetables and whole grain \r\nfoods in our diet may make the things more difficult.A nutritional gap \r\nmay exist between what we eat and what our body requires.Modicare Well \r\nMultivitamin Multimineral provides the necessary nutrients that may help\r\n in bridging the nutritional gap.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;Caution&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Modicare\r\n Well Multivitamin Multimineral is a food supplement and is not indented\r\n to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease. People with specific \r\nmedical conditions, pregnant and lactating women are recommended to \r\nconsult their doctor before taking the dietary supplement.&lt;br&gt;Not recommended for children below 12 years&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h4&gt;FAQ&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Is Well Multivitamin Multimineral a medicine and can cure disease?&lt;br&gt;Well\r\n Multivitamin Multimineral is not a medicine but a food supplement that \r\nprovides essential nutrients and helps in general wellness.Well \r\nMultivitamin Multimineral supplement is not intended to diagnose, treat,\r\n prevent or cure any disease.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',	' WELL MULTIVITAMIN MULTIMINERAL ',	' WELL MULTIVITAMIN MULTIMINERAL ',	' WELL MULTIVITAMIN MULTIMINERAL ',	' WELL MULTIVITAMIN MULTIMINERAL '),
