(104,	1,	'SMOOTH SHAVE GEL ',	'&lt;div id=&quot;accordion0&quot; class=&quot;accordion-section-content open&quot; style=&quot;display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Start your day the manly way.  Luxurious gel with a smooth, top-of-the-world feeling. The perfect beginning you can get!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Velocity Shave Gel has Aloe Vera \r\nextracts that soothe your skin. Vitamin E and Olive Oil tones and \r\nhydrates. Menthol refreshes, revitalizes and leaves skin soft and \r\nsmooth.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;accordion-section-title active&quot; href=&quot;https://www.modicare.com/ProductLanding.aspx?p=pMWa6mCKYSk=&amp;amp;grp=Iey5Mcr6SMI=&amp;amp;pattern=Iey5Mcr6SMI=#accordion1&quot;&gt;grooming tips&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;accordion1&quot; class=&quot;accordion-section-content open&quot; style=&quot;display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Always\r\n try shaving in the direction of hair growth (with the grain) first. \r\nThen for a more closer shave, try shaving against the direction of \r\ngrowth (against the grain)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;',	'SMOOTH SHAVE GEL ',	'SMOOTH SHAVE GEL ',	'SMOOTH SHAVE GEL ',	' SMOOTH SHAVE GEL '),
