t;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Gently cleans &amp;amp; polishes tooth enamel&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Helps&amp;nbsp; remove stains&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Helps prevent cavities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Fights bad breath&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;100% vegetarian&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Attractive metalized packaging&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;accordion-section-title active&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Additional information&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;accordion-section-title active&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Teeth • Healthy Gums • Refreshing&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Breath&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Freshmint&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;Fights bad breath, gives energising freshness and a good mouth feel.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;SPA (Special Polishing Agents)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;Gently polishes your teeth enamel without causing excessive harshness and abrasiveness. Regular use gently removes surface stains caused by tobacco, tea and coffee. Brushing twice a day with Fresh Moments Toothpaste 2 gives you cleaner teeth, healthier gums and fresh breath for long hours.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Xylitol&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;It is known to promote good oral health. Helps prevent bacteria from sticking to the teeth thus reducing plaque and dental cavities and promote healthier enamel.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Fluoride:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Helps in re-mineralisation process and strengthens the enamel layer of the tooth. Helps to prevent cavities &amp;amp; tooth decay.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',	' FRESH MOMENT 2 TOOTH PASTE ',	'FRESH MOMENT 2 TOOTH PASTE ',	' FRESH MOMENT 2 TOOTH PASTE ',	' FRESH MOMENT 2 TOOTH PASTE '),
