(152,	1,	'INTENSE STAY 10 HRS KAJAL ',	'&lt;p&gt;Intense Stay 10 Hrs Kajal is a long wear easy to use retractable pencil \r\nwith a creamy texture that glides on easily to intensify the eyes, makes\r\n them look stunning.&lt;br&gt;It lasts all day and has an excellent color pay off.&lt;br&gt;An ideal choice for anyone who wants the convenience of a pencil liner and a kajal.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;accordion-section-title active&quot; href=&quot;https://www.modicare.com/ProductLanding.aspx?p=FF2EZKTnf8M=&amp;amp;grp=Iey5Mcr6SMI=&amp;amp;pattern=Iey5Mcr6SMI=#accordion1&quot;&gt;features &amp;amp; benefits&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;accordion1&quot; class=&quot;accordion-section-content open&quot; style=&quot;display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;•  10 Hrs stay&lt;br&gt;\r\n•  Creamy texture and easy glide on kajal &lt;br&gt;\r\n•  Retractable tip never needs sharpening. &lt;br&gt;\r\n•  Smudge proof and water proof&lt;br&gt;\r\n•  Can be used as kajal &amp;amp; liner&lt;br&gt;\r\n•  Opthalmologically  tested &lt;br&gt;\r\n•  Made in Germany \r\n&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;accordion-section-title active&quot; href=&quot;https://www.modicare.com/ProductLanding.aspx?p=FF2EZKTnf8M=&amp;amp;grp=Iey5Mcr6SMI=&amp;amp;pattern=Iey5Mcr6SMI=#accordion2&quot;&gt;application&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;accordion2&quot; class=&quot;accordion-section-content open&quot; style=&quot;display: block;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Draw a fine line close to the lower lashes from inner to outer corner of the eyes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;',	' INTENSE STAY 10 HRS KAJAL ',	' INTENSE STAY 10 HRS KAJAL ',	' INTENSE STAY 10 HRS KAJAL ',	' INTENSE STAY 10 HRS KAJAL '),
